  "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-main relative\"\u003e\n \u003ch1 class\u003d\"block text-[4rem] text-[var(--dark)] leading-[4.4rem] font-semibold mb-[5px]\"\u003eH\u0026agrave;n Quốc nổ s\u0026uacute;ng cảnh c\u0026aacute;o 20 binh l\u0026iacute;nh Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n vượt ranh giới qu\u0026acirc;n sự\u003c/h1\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-meta flex items-center flex-wrap flex-row text-[1.3rem] leading-[2rem] font-normal text-[#999] truncate h-[30px] mb-[10px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;:not(:first-child)]:ml-[25px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n   \u003ca href\u003d\"/bao-vietnamnet-vietnamnet-p23.epi\" class\u003d\"bm-card-source flex items-center shrink-0\" title\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o VietnamNet\"\u003e\n    \u003cfigure class\u003d\"image opacity-80 w-auto h-[16px]\" style\u003d\"width:56.25px;height:20px\" aria-label\u003d\"Logo nh\u0026agrave; xuất bản\"\u003e\n     \u003cpicture\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/26dc73b3aef047ae1ee1.png\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/26dc73b3aef047ae1ee1.png\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003cimg src\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/26dc73b3aef047ae1ee1.png\" alt\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o VietnamNet\" width\u003d\"180\" height\u003d\"64\" /\u003e\n     \u003c/picture\u003e\n    \u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n   \u003cspan\u003e\u003cbutton class\u003d\"relative text-[14px] leading-[normal] font-normal text-center cursor-pointer normal-case border-0 transition-button disabled:shadow-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed follow-button flex items-center item-star ml-[10px]\" tabindex\u003d\"0\" type\u003d\"button\" title\u003d\"Theo d\u0026otilde;i \u0026quot;VietnamNet\u0026quot;\" aria-label\u003d\"Button\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-star text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003ctime datetime\u003d\"2025-10-24T03:08:00.000Z\"\u003e24/10/2025\u003c/time\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/jcs-t41375774.epi\" class\u003d\"related inline !text-[#adb5bd] hover:!text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e20\n   \u003c!-- --\u003e li\u0026ecirc;n quan\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/han-quoc-no-sung-canh-cao-20-binh-linh-trieu-tien-vuot-ranh-gioi-quan-su-r53571067.epi\" class\u003d\"origin item-origin\" target\u003d\"_blank\" rel\u003d\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGốc\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003ch3 class\u003d\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\"\u003ePh\u0026iacute;a H\u0026agrave;n Quốc đ\u0026atilde; nổ s\u0026uacute;ng cảnh c\u0026aacute;o sau khi ph\u0026aacute;t hiện khoảng 20 binh sĩ Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n vượt qua ranh giới qu\u0026acirc;n sự li\u0026ecirc;n Triều v\u0026agrave;o cuối tuần qua.\u003c/h3\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [\u0026amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;div]:mb-[15px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTheo Yonhap, Hội đồng Tham mưu trưởng Li\u0026ecirc;n qu\u0026acirc;n \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/han-quoc-tag2475.epi\"\u003eH\u0026agrave;n Quốc\u003c/a\u003e (JCS) tối 23/10 đ\u0026atilde; th\u0026ocirc;ng tin về việc 20 binh sĩ Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n vượt qua ranh giới qu\u0026acirc;n sự trong một thời gian ngắn v\u0026agrave;o cuối tuần qua.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u0026quot;Khoảng 20 binh sĩ \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/trieu-tien-tag552.epi\"\u003eTriều Ti\u0026ecirc;n\u003c/a\u003e đ\u0026atilde; vượt qua Đường Ph\u0026acirc;n chia ranh giới qu\u0026acirc;n sự (MDL) ở gần th\u0026agrave;nh phố Paju v\u0026agrave;o ng\u0026agrave;y 19/10. Qu\u0026acirc;n đội H\u0026agrave;n Quốc đ\u0026atilde; theo d\u0026otilde;i s\u0026aacute;t sao hoạt động của nh\u0026oacute;m l\u0026iacute;nh n\u0026agrave;y, sau đ\u0026oacute; nổ s\u0026uacute;ng cảnh c\u0026aacute;o để buộc họ quay trở lại ph\u0026iacute;a Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n\u0026quot;, đại diện JCS cho biết.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eB\u0026aacute;o c\u0026aacute;o của JCS nhận định, nh\u0026oacute;m binh sĩ Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n c\u0026oacute; thể đ\u0026atilde; v\u0026ocirc; t\u0026igrave;nh vượt qua MDL trong l\u0026uacute;c l\u0026agrave;m việc gần khu vực bi\u0026ecirc;n giới như r\u0026agrave; ph\u0026aacute; m\u0026igrave;n hoặc ph\u0026aacute;t quang đất v\u0026agrave; một số người trong số họ c\u0026oacute; vũ trang.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url(\u0027https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png\u0027)] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\"\u003e\n   \u003ci class\u003d\"icon font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n   \u003cbutton class\u003d\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:416px\"\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"Đường Ph\u0026acirc;n chia ranh giới Qu\u0026acirc;n sự (MDL) ở b\u0026aacute;n đảo Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n. Ảnh: Yonhap\" width\u003d\"625\" height\u003d\"416\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eĐường Ph\u0026acirc;n chia ranh giới Qu\u0026acirc;n sự (MDL) ở b\u0026aacute;n đảo Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n. Ảnh: Yonhap\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTheo JCS, c\u0026oacute; một vụ vượt ranh giới \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/the-gioi.epi\"\u003equ\u0026acirc;n sự\u003c/a\u003e kh\u0026aacute;c cũng xảy ra v\u0026agrave;o ng\u0026agrave;y 19/10 ở khu vực Cheorwon, tỉnh Gangwon. Cụ thể, một binh sĩ Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n đ\u0026atilde; bị qu\u0026acirc;n đội H\u0026agrave;n Quốc bắt giữ sau đ\u0026oacute;, đ\u0026aacute;nh dấu vụ vượt bi\u0026ecirc;n đầu ti\u0026ecirc;n của qu\u0026acirc;n nh\u0026acirc;n Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n kể từ khi Tổng thống H\u0026agrave;n Quốc Lee Jae-myung nhậm chức v\u0026agrave;o th\u0026aacute;ng 6.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u0026quot;Ch\u0026uacute;ng t\u0026ocirc;i kh\u0026ocirc;ng ghi nhận th\u0026ecirc;m động th\u0026aacute;i bất thường n\u0026agrave;o của qu\u0026acirc;n đội Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n sau c\u0026aacute;c vụ việc tr\u0026ecirc;n. Hai sự cố dường như kh\u0026ocirc;ng c\u0026oacute; mối li\u0026ecirc;n hệ trực tiếp, do xảy ra ở những vị tr\u0026iacute; v\u0026agrave; thời điểm kh\u0026aacute;c nhau. Qu\u0026acirc;n đội H\u0026agrave;n Quốc đang theo d\u0026otilde;i chặt chẽ c\u0026aacute;c hoạt động của Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n v\u0026agrave; thực hiện c\u0026aacute;c biện ph\u0026aacute;p cần thiết theo quy tr\u0026igrave;nh t\u0026aacute;c chiến\u0026quot;, JCS th\u0026ocirc;ng tin.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text body-author text-right\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e Việt Dũng \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp\" tabindex\u003d\"-1\" role\u003d\"dialog\" aria-hidden\u003d\"true\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__bg\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__scroll-wrap\"\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__container\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__top-bar\"\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__counter\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--close\" title\u003d\"Close (Esc)\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--share\" title\u003d\"Share\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--fs\" title\u003d\"Toggle fullscreen\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--zoom\" title\u003d\"Zoom in/out\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__icn\"\u003e\n       \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__cut\"\u003e\n        \u00